headline: Clearing ‘Aged’ Inventory, Stabilizing China Business Are Top Priorities for Caleres as it Aims to Breakeven on Stuart Weitzman in 2026
summary: CEO Jay Schmidt gave analysts a closer look at the work being done to transition Stuart Weitzman into the company following the acquisition's close in August.
